                     <interp inst="t18200918-234-person2241" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman. I heard the cry<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182009180092"></xptr>of watch, ran up, and found a dozen or more round the prosecutor, who was holding the prisoner. He gave charge of her, and gave the account he has now.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. He took me home, and gave me the handkerchief instead of money.</p>
               <p>PIZZEY. It is false.</p>
